# Freyra UI Standards

## File Structure

All UI code lives in `ui/` -- never edit the old `webui.py`.

```
ui/
  app.py           -- Main Blocks layout, generation wiring
  theme.py         -- Custom dark theme with amber accents
  constants.py     -- UI constants
  pages/
    campaign.py    -- Campaign batch generation tab
    gallery.py     -- Smart gallery with export
  components/
    vram_indicator.py -- Real-time VRAM bar
```

## Design Language

- Dark mode primary, amber/gold (#c4852e) accents
- Luxury creative aesthetic -- generous spacing, clean typography
- Mobile-responsive (must work in Colab iframe)

## Component Patterns

Every creative dimension follows this pattern:

```python
with gr.Accordion('Dimension Name', open=False, elem_classes=['dimension-section']):
    dropdown = gr.Dropdown(label='Select X', choices=options, value=NONE_OPTION)
    custom = gr.Textbox(label='Custom X', placeholder='Or describe your own...')
```

## Rules

- Use `gr.update()` for conditional visibility, never recreate components
- Font families must be lists: `[gr.themes.GoogleFont("Inter"), "sans-serif"]`
- No circular imports -- `ui/app.py` must not import `launch.py`
- Wire events with `queue=False, show_progress='hidden'` for instant UI responses
- Generation events use `.then()` chaining for sequential steps
